✅ Verify Routing Table

On any router:

R1# show ip route

You should see routes marked with:

R 30.0.0.0 [120/1] via 20.0.0.2
R 40.0.0.0 [120/2] via 20.0.0.2
R 50.0.0.0 [120/3] via 20.0.0.2

👉 120 = Administrative Distance of RIP
👉 Number after slash = Hop count

